# Run the Container Image

If container automation is enabled for this project, the repository includes a
`Dockerfile` and can publish images to GitHub Container Registry on tagged
releases.

## Build the image locally

```bash
docker build -t {{ repository_name }} .
```

## Run the CLI from the image

```bash
docker run --rm {{ repository_name }} --version
```

## Published image location

Published images use the GitHub Container Registry name:

```text
ghcr.io/{{ repository_namespace }}/{{ repository_name }}
```
